*                               NUMBER = '000'
*                               V1 = LS_KEY-MeasurePoint
*                             SEVERITY = IF_ABAP_BEHV_MESSAGE=>SEVERITY-SUCCESS ) %ELEMENT-%FIELD-MeasurePoint = IF_ABAP_BEHV=>MK-ON )  ).
*
*      MOVE-CORRESPONDING LT_REPORTED-ZI_PM_PRIDE_ROUTE_MP_TEMP_M TO REPORTED-ZI_PM_PRIDE_ROUTE_MP_TEMP_M.
